  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365470/extras/009c836a6f5e0615fb3c427f6b43093b.poster.avif?t=1772833720\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365470/extras/009c836a6f5e0615fb3c427f6b43093b.webm?t=1772833720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365470/extras/009c836a6f5e0615fb3c427f6b43093b.mp4?t=1772833720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A nostalgic road trip on an endless highway, driving iconic '80s cars through a neon-filled paradise. Let the synthwave/retrowave soundtrack guide you toward the horizon, leading you into a world of nostalgic vibes.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The road stretches infinitely, taking you back to a simpler time, where palm trees sway gently in the warm breeze. As the rhythm takes over, you enter a state of serene reflection, racing through a universe where time is measured in moments of calm and nostalgia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you accelerate, you'll unlock new worlds and over 15 iconic vehicles, each offering customization options and upgrades. For competitive players, each world features an online leaderboard, allowing you to compete globally or with friends for the highest scores.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365470/extras/d89e13fb8b75800b8da970e54e6efe3a.poster.avif?t=1772833720\" width=616 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365470/extras/d89e13fb8b75800b8da970e54e6efe3a.webm?t=1772833720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365470/extras/d89e13fb8b75800b8da970e54e6efe3a.mp4?t=1772833720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 15 Vehicles </strong>: Each with unique characteristics and a first-person view.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Soundtrack </strong>: An extensive library of Synthwave/Vaporwave/Retrowave tracks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay </strong>: 5 different game modes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Garage </strong>: Personalize it your way, by changing the flooring and wallpaper, as well as decorative objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vehicles :</strong> Acquire new vehicles and improve your performance, as well as customize them the way you want.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scenery</strong>: Explore over 10 worlds, each offering different atmospheres and feelings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rain Mode :</strong> Want more vibes? Or just chill with the sound of rain on your windshield.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Custom Music</strong> : Load up your own songs and drive to your perfect playlist.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards </strong>: Chase high scores on global and friends' leaderboards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cool Vibes </strong>: Brings back fond memories of simpler times. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365470/extras/009c836a6f5e0615fb3c427f6b43093b.poster.avif?t=1772833720\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365470/extras/009c836a6f5e0615fb3c427f6b43093b.webm?t=1772833720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365470/extras/009c836a6f5e0615fb3c427f6b43093b.mp4?t=1772833720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A nostalgic road trip on an endless highway, driving iconic '80s cars through a neon-filled paradise. Let the synthwave/retrowave soundtrack guide you toward the horizon, leading you into a world of nostalgic vibes.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The road stretches infinitely, taking you back to a simpler time, where palm trees sway gently in the warm breeze. As the rhythm takes over, you enter a state of serene reflection, racing through a universe where time is measured in moments of calm and nostalgia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you accelerate, you'll unlock new worlds and over 15 iconic vehicles, each offering customization options and upgrades. For competitive players, each world features an online leaderboard, allowing you to compete globally or with friends for the highest scores.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365470/extras/d89e13fb8b75800b8da970e54e6efe3a.poster.avif?t=1772833720\" width=616 height=40 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365470/extras/d89e13fb8b75800b8da970e54e6efe3a.webm?t=1772833720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365470/extras/d89e13fb8b75800b8da970e54e6efe3a.mp4?t=1772833720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 15 Vehicles </strong>: Each with unique characteristics and a first-person view.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Soundtrack </strong>: An extensive library of Synthwave/Vaporwave/Retrowave tracks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay </strong>: 5 different game modes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Garage </strong>: Personalize it your way, by changing the flooring and wallpaper, as well as decorative objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vehicles :</strong> Acquire new vehicles and improve your performance, as well as customize them the way you want.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scenery</strong>: Explore over 10 worlds, each offering different atmospheres and feelings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rain Mode :</strong> Want more vibes? Or just chill with the sound of rain on your windshield.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Custom Music</strong> : Load up your own songs and drive to your perfect playlist.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards </strong>: Chase high scores on global and friends' leaderboards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cool Vibes </strong>: Brings back fond memories of simpler times. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
